translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  39,75,"Ni tinchaona Achimalaika achisyungulaga mungulugulu mwa Arishi (Chindanda Chaulungu) aku ali nkuluswejesya lumbili lwa M’mbuje gwao (Allah). Ni kuchijilanyisyidwa chilikati chao mwakuonaonape, ni kuchiŵechetedwa yanti: “Lumbili losope lwene alapikwe Allah M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  40,1,Hâ. Mîm
  40,2,"Kutulusyidwa kwa Chitabu (Qur’an) kukuumila kwa Allah, Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwakumanyilila nnope"
  40,3,"Jwakululuka sambi ni Jwakupochela toba, Jwaukali pakupeleka ipotesi, Nsyene kupeleka mituka jejinji, pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwalakwe, soni Kukwakwe pe ni kwakuujila"
  40,4,"Ngaakasakanganaga pa ma Ȃya ga Allah ikaŵeje aŵala ŵaakufuulu, basi kukannyenga kwendajenda kwao mu ilambo (kupita nchisosa yaakusaka mwantunjelele, chisimu mbesi jao ni ku Moto)"
  40,5,"Ŵaakaaniile paujo pao ŵandu ŵa Nuhu kwisa soni mikutula (jine) panyuma pao, sano umati uliose wasachilile (yangalumbana) kwa ntenga jwao kuti ankwembekanye (am’bulaje), ni ŵakanganile ni yaunami kuti atyochesye nayo yakuona, basi nakwembekenye. Ana ipotesi Yangu yaliji uli"
  40,6,Soni iyyoyopeyo lisimichiche liloŵe lya Ambuje ŵenu pa aŵala ŵakanile lyanti ŵanganyao ni ŵandu ŵa ku Moto
  40,7,"Aŵala (Achimalaika) ŵaakutwichila Arishi (Chindanda Chaulungu) ni ŵali mungulugulu mwakwe, akuluswejesyaga lumbili lwa M’mbuje gwao (Allah), ni akunkulupililaga Jwalakwe, ni akwaŵendelaga chikululuko aŵala ŵaakulupilile (achitiji): “Ambuje ŵetu! Nchijenele chindu chilichose pa ukoto ni umanyilisi, basi mwakululuchilani aŵala ŵatesile toba ni kuya litala Lyenu, ni mwagosani ku ilagasyo ya Moto Waukali.”"